{"tid":673789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《金剛經》、《四十二章經》變生財工具，淪為廢紙作回收之用","createTime":"2018-05-22T06:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T05:15:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3b03ef2e50ee6a06d437482d2ef7ba288de30f32","tid":673789,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"正值佛誕，數百本佛經被放街頭免費任攞，部分淪為廢紙作回收之用。有市民今早(22日)在牛頭角港鐵站對出，見到數百本《金剛經》、《四十二章經》等佛經隨地擺放，原意是讓有心人與佛結緣，認識佛法，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>卻有長者用紅白藍袋狂擸數十本用作回收廢紙之用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span>，質疑助印佛經者「好心做壞事」，佛經被當生財工具甚至是垃圾，求緣不成反而對經書褻瀆不敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180522/photo/bkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180522112428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180522112428&h=71b67ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">數百本佛經被放在街頭，部分被人拿去當廢紙回收。(讀者提供)</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180522/bkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180522%2Fbkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001.html&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=d3abf186\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180522/bkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"ee806ef09e7e60b56e41418defc84b6edf4395d1","tid":673789,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"本身是佛教徒的市民張小姐指出，不少人想求緣，或者消業障，會自行找喜歡的經書版本，並與出版社接洽印佛經，再把佛經轉贈他人，但有助印人責任心不足，只要求出版社順手把經書送出，出版社便把經書隨便放街頭免費任攞，她以往亦見過上址有大堆經書擺放。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180522/photo/bkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180522112428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180522102533942-0522_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180522112428&h=f0931bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">該數百本佛經有不同版本。(讀者提供)</span></div><br />\n<br />\n張小姐直言，看到此情況感到傷心及失望，「呢啲經書係『法寶』，好唔開心『法寶』畀人咁浪費。」她指佛教徒非常尊重法寶，佛經不能亂放，希望助印人印好經書後作適當安排，送給有緣人。"},{"pid":"a085e6e63c7cc5ecbbb98585faf26d8c79d82e1a","tid":673789,"uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"廢老都係無神論者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實廢老心態上驚唔驚死左之後既世界係點<br />\n為左幾蚊就一D都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係耶老?"},{"pid":"b529753def610ebcea904abcd200d4ec5e5b2bea","tid":673789,"uid":90863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"啲書唔知要斬幾多棵樹先印到呢？斬樹算唔算殺生？"},{"pid":"cb91ccf58cbfc6192694b44489634f7f01800071","tid":673789,"uid":147314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"四十二章經唔係得八本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c7166c6b5f26dca8589ecc66a8d95cc7b6f93c","tid":673789,"uid":294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:09:23.000Z","msg":"係人都知寶藏喺東郊皇陵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲買黎做乜"},{"pid":"dc026170e5a5d516851856f28a61155b7f9088f2","tid":673789,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10c7166c6b5f26dca8589ecc66a8d95cc7b6f93c","tid":673789,"uid":294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:09:23.000Z","msg":"係人都知寶藏喺東郊皇陵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲買黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"鹿鼎山好似都有寶藏"},{"pid":"9d7e0322e005e5a48d5d2fd13c6d19bc6ba1eac1","tid":673789,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會有易筋經同九陽神功係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ab539bc43c2f798e8044b8dce2423aefedbe61","tid":673789,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"倩女抓癢<br />\n黑山姥姥：金剛經"}]}